headline: Cognizant Schedules Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings Release and Conference Call
summary: TEANECK, N.J., Jan. 15, 2025 /PRNewswire/ -- Cognizant , a leading provider of information technology, consulting, and business process services, will announce results for the fourth quarter of 2024...
